{"tid":87934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘綫又壞，垃圾","createTime":"2017-01-20T08:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T09:36:19.000Z","uid":18381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8597cbf21b2b79cffd6dfaaf9974fa0e6d4b5050","tid":87934,"uid":18381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:16:26.000Z","msg":"下午3時37分，由於何文田站附近有訊號故障，觀塘綫列車駛經油麻地站至何文田站路段時需要慢駛，觀塘綫來往黃埔站及調景嶺站的行車時間預計需要額外10-15分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n現時觀塘綫月台上的乘客較多，候車時間亦會較長，港鐵呼籲乘客預留充裕時間。港鐵職員現正進行搶修工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170120&amp;guid=56199217&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170120%26guid%3D56199217%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=saMSncSJMX0EtbMXlfI9jgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=ebcdde7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170120%26guid%3D56199217%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=cce00624\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170120&amp;guid=56199217&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441eb1b784cb3743a11744d2efff865365e7984b","tid":87934,"uid":75358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T09:36:19.000Z","msg":"99%準時率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}